Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.80,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.78,0:03:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.95,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, 10 years ago, in the East Blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.78,0:03:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.90,0:03:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.33,0:04:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Where can freedom be found? \NA Sad Departure of a Boy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.64,0:04:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.70,0:04:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you sea cretin!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.30,0:04:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go of Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.10,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.23,0:04:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally we found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are pretty serious \Nwounds, Luffy! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.95,0:04:45.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see Sabo anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.76,0:04:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo went home. He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.33,0:04:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.62,0:05:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the boss monkey from Mt. Corvo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the mountain bandit - Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.29,0:05:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why but I'm registered \Nas their foster parent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.98,0:05:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't stand by and watch someone \Ntry to take my boys' lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.56,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if I'm not their real parent!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.20,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just let you go if you back away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.92,0:05:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll have \Nto resort to violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? Alright then...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.03,0:05:49.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.62,0:05:51.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.20,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you saying, Ace?! \NDon't try to fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bluejam is a real villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a guy that a kid like you can beat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--L-Let me fight, too!\N--No, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all, why don't you \Ntake Luffy and go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.37,0:06:36.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take responsibility \Nfor bringing Ace home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Y-Yes, ma'am!\N--Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! Come home safely!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman and a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.64,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you overestimate your \Nability, you'll only get hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.31,0:07:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the strong and the \Ncowardly survive in wars!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The brave always die.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.70,0:07:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a dead man! The fire \Nis all over the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.01,0:07:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could this happen all of the sudden?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's hot! It's hot!\N--There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.23,0:07:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.32,0:08:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.21,0:08:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The explosion left a path!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.46,0:08:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what's going \Non but this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.88,0:08:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey look, there is a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.71,0:08:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This path leads up to the shore!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get away by following it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.20,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go before the fire returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.78,0:08:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How awful they are to burn the \Narea and the residents there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,how did you know the situation in such \Nan outlying country in the East Blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.55,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something special \Nabout this country?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country is an example of how \Nthe world will be in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.41,0:09:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There can be no happiness in a world
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.13,0:09:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwhere the undesirables are thrown away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I will change the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:16.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay here... I'll never be free!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even in a country like \Nthis, there are children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.26,0:09:41.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those of you who are willing to \Nfight for freedom, come aboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:49.40,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,GOA KINGDOM "ROYAL PALACE"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:54.36,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,HIGH TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did they find Sabo?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.45,0:10:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called in the military. \NThey'll find him soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.83,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Sabo is giving us \Na hard time, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.05,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this town really safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like the fire will \Nengulf the town any minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.49,0:10:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there any way to enter High Town?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even allow a bug \Nto enter - nobles only!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Boss!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:44.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.46,0:10:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Dadan didn't return \Nfrom the burning Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, wait, Luffy. You're not \Nrecovered - where're you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.31,0:11:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go and look for Ace and Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.20,0:11:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:25.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's what I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously wounded. You \Nhave to rest nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.13,0:11:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a lot of troops \Nin the Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.72,0:11:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to take care of the mess after the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just burned junk \Nthat they're throing out,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.80,0:11:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but survivors, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna kill you if you go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.44,0:11:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.99,0:12:10.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that Sabo is worrying about us, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.91,0:12:15.54,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,THE FORMER SITE OF THE GRAY TERMINAL
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.75,0:12:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a great view!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:23.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a pain in the butt \Nto clean up this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we find a survivor, we're \Nto shoot them on sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.96,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there aren't as many dead \Nbodies as I thought there'd be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.78,0:12:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a big fire. It could've \Nburned out the bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was nervous yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.77,0:12:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that the \Nfire might get to this side of the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.37,0:12:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that Bluejam's \Nship was on fire, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.34,0:12:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice to know that \Nthose villains got burned!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi! it's a nice day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is a lovely morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.17,0:13:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are still so many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough with this game of tag, okay boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.53,0:14:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times you \Nrun, you can't get away, Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.94,0:14:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the police and troops \Nhave a picture of you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.75,0:14:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never get out of High Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or even out of this house!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two, change your uniforms and \Nstart working here as guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.67,0:14:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we have our duties...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.73,0:14:40.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is nothing that a nobleman can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.54,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get the approval of your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo, you must barricade \Nyourself in your room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.92,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and educate yourself in your role as a noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.38,0:14:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.70,0:15:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, I can make things \Nhappen just by giving the word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can take care of \Nyou or those two easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.24,0:15:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.13,0:15:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you mend your ways \Nand study hard like Stelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:27.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...study so that you can make your parents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who brought you into the world, happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because that will make you happy, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.29,0:15:44.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I'm here for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.30,0:15:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so dependable, Stelly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, Let me buy you some luxurious clothes
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the ceremony the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, we'll see the \NCelestial Dragon in person!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... helpless!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.96,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll check your homework tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.33,0:16:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, have a nice day!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.08,0:16:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that you died in the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.74,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are okay, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I'll put you guys in \Ndanger if I try to see you now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.48,0:17:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is like a birdcage!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can stand living in \Nthis country filled with stale air.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is freedom?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.63,0:17:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where can I find it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.57,0:17:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shift is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the time already?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be sleeping on the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. By the way, how \Nare things in the town?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ceremony is just a day away, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.56,0:17:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy. People are going \Nwild getting ready for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.56,0:17:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What bad luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:18:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a once-in-a-lifetime \Nthing but I got to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.76,0:18:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This boy and I will be the only \Ntwo in this house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the Celestial Dragon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It depends on your attitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.53,0:18:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the citizens will be \Nat the harbor tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.82,0:18:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be such a pain to stand guard there,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,compared with this baby-sitting gig!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.26,0:18:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, why don't you take my place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.21,0:18:28.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.04,0:18:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.70,0:18:37.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take good care of Sabo.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.32,0:19:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day of the World Noble \Nfrom the Grand Line's visit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.58,0:19:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Goa Kingdom has arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A lavish ceremony is prepared \Nfor the arrival of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.44,0:19:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ring, ring, ring... Ring, \Nring, ring... Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.72,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, this is A-team on the coast.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Celestial Dragon's ship \Nwill arrive in a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.49,0:19:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger that. It's all quiet here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.00,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll continue to stand guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.36,0:19:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clank!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.58,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look! There is a ship leaving port!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?\N--Is it a fishing boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Come back here! Don't get \Nin the way of the ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a child! There's a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child? I wonder which family he's from.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.99,0:20:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A child?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.44,0:20:17.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honey, could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.73,0:20:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible! The \Nguard is looking after him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a nice day! It's \Nperfect for setting sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.31,0:20:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That's mine! Somebody \Nstole my fish boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! He has a black flag on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.84,0:20:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he think that he's a pirate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! A kid can't just become a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.71,0:21:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where is he heading?\N--He's disrupting the ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's ship will arrive soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.66,0:21:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.13,0:21:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.35,0:21:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kid, come back here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The scariest fate for me is to \Nlose myself in this country and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.40,0:21:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,turn into someone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.61,0:21:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Sabo on that ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.06,0:21:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Government's ship is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.16,0:22:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ship is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll die if I crash into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.31,0:22:07.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's avoid that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.68,0:22:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. He's turning away.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.33,0:22:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the commoners are welcoming us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.93,0:22:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're so blessed that \Nit's rare to even see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.24,0:22:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that a real \NCelestial Dragon is on that ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.29,0:22:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like a fish boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.95,0:22:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice to be captain \Nof a ship like that someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.54,0:22:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude is that!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fishing boat has been hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.44,0:23:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace and Dadan return to their hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.39,0:23:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As everyone is rejoicing \Nover their safe return,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.64,0:23:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they learn of the tragedy \Nthat struck Sabo at the port.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.36,0:23:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing with sympathy \Nwhat Sabo had tried to do,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.12,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are befallen \Nby regret and grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take Good Care of Him! A \NLetter from the Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.01,0:23:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
