Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After losing his brother Ace during \Nthe War of the Best against the Navy,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was consumed with unbearable sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.10,0:03:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is, however, an untold \Nstory of the brothers...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...10 years ago in the East \NBlue - Luffy and Ace as boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.56,0:04:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Take Good Care of Him! A \NLetter from the Brother!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.51,0:04:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace is not dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.03,0:04:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, I know. I know how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too risky to go to Gray Terminal now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.55,0:04:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since you're wounded and \Nthere are troops everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...!\N--It was a big fire! And chances are...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.03,0:04:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...slim but we all want to believe \Nthat the boss and Ace are alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.63,0:04:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra went there to look for \Nthem now so trust him and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.03,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody's having a hard \Ntime - not just you, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--The fishing boat has been hit!\N--How's the child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.88,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He made the Celestial Dragon mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.13,0:04:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! The ship is catching fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did they shoot me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saint Jalmack! There is a child on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:58.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When someone flies a black flag, he's \Na pirate regardless of who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.34,0:05:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But most importantly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.23,0:05:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A commoner shouldn't cross \Nthe path of my ship!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What was that ship doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important ceremony!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.20,0:05:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't \Nwanna put the Celestial Dragon in a bad mood!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.65,0:05:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move the shipwreck already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.05,0:06:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey guys, those two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.13,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace... Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.25,0:06:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's severely wounded! \NHurry up and treat her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that I was dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.14,0:06:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...!\N--Why are you crying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not dead, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.47,0:07:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Easy, easy, that's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is just happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.86,0:07:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I ask you about the night of the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After we left with Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.53,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what happened to you and boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought against Bluejam...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.91,0:07:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we barely defeated him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.39,0:08:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we tried to follow you guys right away
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the fire was blocking our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.00,0:08:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! There's no way out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Wait!\N--What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.55,0:08:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no choice since I told them
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.63,0:08:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'd take responsibility \Nfor bringing you home...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.24,0:08:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow my lead. Don't get \Nseparated at any cost!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.65,0:08:28.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dadan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Dadan! Are you alright, Dadan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally made it through the fire
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nbut Dadan got severely burned.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We managed to get to the riverside \Nin the In-Between Forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:09:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! You can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.47,0:09:04.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.60,0:09:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the town to steal some \Nmedicine and get something to eat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.57,0:09:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tried to save Dadan's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry \Nabout me so just go, Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.48,0:09:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap! I thought you were \Nresponsible for bringing me home!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.17,0:09:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't allow you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some survivors could be around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anyone get away! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.85,0:09:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, okay, we see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.69,0:09:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, \NI'm glad that you both survived!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.94,0:09:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry that I made you worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what \Nhappened to Gray Terminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Sabo is worrying about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Banzai!\N--Banzai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.91,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another rude commoner could \Nappear at any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Watch carefully.\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.02,0:10:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how's Sabo doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad that Ace is back \Nand Dadan is recovering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, at that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.85,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't run!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help getting fired up sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.23,0:10:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always afraid that if I run,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.12,0:10:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave something important behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.95,0:10:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.52,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy was behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.67,0:10:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know but I think that's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.67,0:10:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when he faced a cloud \Nof enemies beyond his power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger would never run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.59,0:11:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was he suicidal? Running \Naway is a strategy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.85,0:11:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right but he'd never do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.00,0:11:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he'd leave the \Npeople he loved behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he ran, he would put his crew in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, "he wouldn't run \Naway" isn't quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.32,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't let the enemy have \Na chance to go after his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.95,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd change into a sort of \Ndemon in those situations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He once destroyed a country's entire military
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because they talked badly about his crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.72,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'd become violent when angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NHe was short-tempered and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.74,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he was naive and straightforward \Nlike a child at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because his early life was like Ace's.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hated to lose those he loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was that reckless but he survived,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.92,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and became the King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:12:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although he got a bad reputation, \Nhis crew trusted him implicitly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.53,0:12:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I as a Navy soldier \Ncouldn't help respecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to take care of Ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.21,0:12:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the ones taking care of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.21,0:12:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Have something you want to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.01,0:12:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the world still hate Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:25.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And while Ace hates his father,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it really is "like father, like son."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.76,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's see which \None of you will win...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.60,0:12:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dogra!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were looking for Ace and Dadan, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah? That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What?! Sabo is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.79,0:12:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop lying, you fool! \NDon't even joke about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying or joking \Nabout it! It was so sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could barely believe what I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.46,0:13:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.59,0:13:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Sabo went back to his family's home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could he be at sea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.64,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! He went home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hoodlum like me can \Nunderstand how he feels!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People don't always wanna \Ngo back to their home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he was really happy, \Nhe wouldn't go out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.90,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't go out to sea by himself \Nwith a black flag on his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.84,0:13:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was all by myself even if I had parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why didn't we go \Nthere to take him back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:14:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the guy who killed \NSabo now?! I'm gonna kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.27,0:14:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,K-Kill the Celestial Dragon?! \NThat's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.90,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you little shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.83,0:14:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so confident even \Nthough you're not that strong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do?! They'll just kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.46,0:14:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll die and people will \Nforget you by tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.86,0:14:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just a nameless kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was killed by this country! This world!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.01,0:14:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you do about it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your father changed the world by his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.60,0:14:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you become a man that important,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you can do whatever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tie this fool up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:15:02.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Stop crying like a girl, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to your senses, Ace?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Untie him.\N--Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.72,0:15:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Where's Luffy?\N--He's been crying all night and he's sleeping now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.21,0:15:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boss! You're not gonna believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.26,0:15:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We got a letter from Sabo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.34,0:15:58.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,TO MY BROTHERS AT MT. CORVO FROM SABO
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He must've sent it before he went out to sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.72,0:16:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna go to the town! \NIt's for us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:16.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Ace, Luffy, I hope you guys \Nweren't hurt in the fire."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm worrying about you both but \NI believe that you're okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.00,0:16:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm sorry to say it, guys, but when you \Nget this letter, I'll already be..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...out on the sea."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.74,0:16:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Things led to things and I decided \Nto set out to sea before you."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.01,0:16:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"My destination will be anywhere but here."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm gonna become stronger \Nand become a pirate!"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.23,0:16:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The three of us have to become \Nthe freest pirates ever."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"One day, let's meet up again somewhere."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:17:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Somewhere on the wide open sea! \NDefinitely, someday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"By the way, Ace, which of us \Ndo you think is the bigger brother?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.70,0:17:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Two big brothers and one little brother."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"It's odd but our brotherhood \Nis my treasure."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.43,0:17:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Luffy is still a weak crybaby but..."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"...he is our little brother \Nso take good care of him!"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.94,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could they call themselves \Nobservers?! They're partying everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't covered Sabo's story...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.35,0:18:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that his parents didn't take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.99,0:18:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His parents are nobles
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:24.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they're powerless against the World \NGovernment and Celestial Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Luffy doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He still isn't eating much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he still eats twice as much as we do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Sabo's death really got to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.07,0:19:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.42,0:19:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta set out to sea someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.58,0:19:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get out of this \Ncountry and live freely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.36,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we're brothers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.78,0:19:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer are you gonna lie there?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The treasure that we were hiding \Nin the forest is all gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.36,0:19:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The survivors from Bluejam's crew took \Nit or maybe the military found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.79,0:19:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where it went.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:20:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't care about the treasure anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.12,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the pirate savings that \NI was gonna share with Sabo
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but Sabo didn't need it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'll just let it go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.14,0:20:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no use having treasure \Nif you can't even protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.20,0:20:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Ace... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.16,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More, more and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.51,0:20:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More and more, more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna become even stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I can protect anything or anyone! \NI don't have to lose anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.43,0:20:57.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace, please don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out! Worry about yourself first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.53,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're far weaker than me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen carefully, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.30,0:21:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo told me to take care of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.85,0:21:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I promise that I'll never die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I leave a wimpy \Nbrother like you behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh... Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not smart so I don't quite \Nknow what really killed Sabo yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.16,0:21:40.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it must be something opposed to freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo died before he knew freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We exchanged that same cup \Nof sake and we're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to live without leaving any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.62,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.96,0:22:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boys from noble family...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will become full nobles when they turn 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.28,0:22:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I need to leave here by 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.71,0:22:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta go out to sea someday...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and live as we like. \NFreer than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.19,0:22:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.01,0:22:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means we'll make enemies of many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.96,0:22:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the old man will become our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.23,0:22:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You gotta risk everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.47,0:22:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out to sea at 17!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.23,0:22:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we will become... pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.49,0:23:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy and Ace are stricken with grief,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.09,0:23:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they hold on to their \Ndream of becoming pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.15,0:23:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and set off toward the future again.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their day of departure will come...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.47,0:23:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To achieve the dream that \NSabo was unable to realize!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.48,0:23:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.96,0:23:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"To Live Up to the Promise! \NDepartures of Their Own!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.11,0:23:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
