Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is the Great Pirate Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.94,0:02:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Countless pirates fight \Ndesperately for the One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great treasure left behind by \NGold Roger, King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned \Nto rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.68,0:03:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,also takes to the sea to become \Nthe next King of the Pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.47,0:03:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Luffy and his friends \Novercome numerous adventures,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the World Government is less and \Nless able to ignore their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is exciting!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of adventure \Nis waiting for us next?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crew, on its way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will speed along the Grand Line again today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:36.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,10 years ago in the East Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there were 3 boys who dreamed \Nof becoming pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.49,0:03:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First, Sabo set sail and then Ace \Nwent out to sea 7 years later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:48.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Luffy! I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And 3 years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy departed \Nfrom his hometown - Windmill Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.53,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sabo was first and Ace was second.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.11,0:04:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm third but I'm gonna top them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.82,0:04:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll catch up with you soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, Luffy is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.94,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The King of the Pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.57,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.44,0:04:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...weak!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.88,0:04:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I Want to See Them! Luffy's Mournful Cry!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.96,0:04:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go along the Grand Line!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.86,0:04:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna take over the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:42.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with that island!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.33,0:04:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me cannonballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.05,0:04:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meteor Fist Shower!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.93,0:04:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, here, here, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:03.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've had enough for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's Garp-san!\N--Garp-san is back with his ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.80,0:05:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On business?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:18.08,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"EAST BLUE" GOA KINGDOM--WINDMILL VILLAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.60,0:05:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san, I've read about \Nthe war in the newspaper!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said it was a great victory for the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, how is everybody here doing?\N--What happened to Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's gonna happen to the world \Nafter Whitebeard's death, Garp-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.60,0:05:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen pirate ships offshore \Nfrequently over the past few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.16,0:05:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't even sleep in peace at night \Nbecause we fear their invasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! I just sank \Nthree of them out at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:52.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were all amateurs who \Ndon't even know how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:06:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the seas will be uneasy all over the \Nworld because Whitebeard was a deterrent.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.01,0:06:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a remote village in the East \NBlue but you have to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.16,0:06:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey!\N--Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.51,0:06:15.93,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SECURITY BY NAVY VICE ADMIRAL GARP
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Security by Navy Vice Admiral \NGarp"? Oh, I feel safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.00,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have to be afraid of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san, we have another problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.98,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain bandits came down to the village
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.72,0:06:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they're taking over Makino's bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain bandits?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.36,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! You can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.16,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:40.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you come back \Nand show your face here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vice Admiral Garp!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of it! I know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there at the battlefield...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.62,0:07:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there with them! \NWhat did you do to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.64,0:07:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to help?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?! Why?! Why?! Why?! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.08,0:07:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you stand by and watch Ace die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You chose your job over your family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.67,0:07:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Garp! You're the hero of the Navy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.22,0:07:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, you old bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.20,0:07:39.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Easy, easy, boss, stop it!\N--Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp, say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.48,0:07:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you help him?! Why \Ndidn't you do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get on your feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.51,0:07:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cold-blooded scum!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.67,0:07:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, Dadan-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makino...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see that he's taking \Nit harder than anybody else
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he couldn't help them \Neven though he was there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.20,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's having a harder time than anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:09:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's start today's lesson \Nof how to express gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.31,0:09:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, let's get started already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.68,0:09:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you got it, Ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.76,0:09:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.28,0:09:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say "Thank you \Nin advance" on that occasion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:15.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that wasn't right? \NIt sounded cool though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.24,0:09:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ace-kun wants to learn this
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because he \Nwants to say "thank you" properly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.37,0:09:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to the captain of the Red-Haired \NPirates who helped Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Shanks?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will be a pirate by \Nthe time I see Red-Haired.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a pirate and as your old \Nbrother, it's my job to thank him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:43.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's do it pretending that \Nhe's right in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ace. Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:50.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booh! That's not right. It's \Nnot nice to say "the hell."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it "Who the heck are you"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.48,0:09:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.28,0:09:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say "you fool"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you, you bastard?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Whom" is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Booh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it! Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're bugging me by saying \Nstupid things! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Ace, I found an anaconda's \Nnest filled with big eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.68,0:10:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go get some now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Big eggs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.78,0:10:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna learn how to pay respect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.57,0:10:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could get hurt if no one's \Nthere and the anaconda finds me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.45,0:10:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll be safe if you come with me! So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.80,0:10:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved his brother so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.22,0:11:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makino!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Garp.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It said in the newspaper \Nthat he went missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.97,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He got away by submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.12,0:11:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Navy went after him in full force \Nand searched for him desperately
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they didn't find any shipwreck.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he's probably alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how does Navy Vice Admiral \NGarp-san know the mountain bandit?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.64,0:11:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is so stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll take his side no matter \Nwhat kind of pirate he becomes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.99,0:12:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It breaks my heart when I think \Nabout how he must feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be defeated!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.13,0:12:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, far away in the \Nsecond half of the Grand Line -
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the New World...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Red-Haired,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've no words to express my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.74,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I always respected Whitebeard, \Neven though he was my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.71,0:13:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even Sengoku respected him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whitebeard, Ace...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us handle the burial of those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:35.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree! I will take the blame on myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.54,0:13:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, we should go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.60,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy must be having a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.46,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe what Ace did.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.01,0:13:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take back what you just said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.85,0:14:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make fun of the man who saved me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.27,0:14:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of this era should be "Whitebeard"!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what Captain Roger would've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.48,0:14:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted the captain to run away sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:25.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and be able to shed tears.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.72,0:14:32.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.42,0:14:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By experiencing both victory and defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,running away and shedding tears,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a man will become a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:15:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you have to move on!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.98,0:15:24.94,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"CALM BELT" MAIDEN ISLAND
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm too weak! I can't save anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.14,0:15:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.01,0:15:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.22,0:15:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.85,0:15:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just watch you hurt yourself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my own body! It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.42,0:16:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you can't blame Ace \Nfor doing what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His death was not your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, you bastard! I'm gonna \Nbeat you if you say another word!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it if it makes you happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.15,0:16:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm injured too but I'm not gonna \Nget beaten by you in that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.67,0:16:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:16:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jimbei...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.01,0:17:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was going after Teach,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw my brother for the first time \Nin 3 years in Alabasta Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.55,0:17:15.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I felt relieved instantly as I saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.19,0:17:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, you brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see things clearly now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believed that you \Ncould overcome anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you've never doubted your strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But all those formidable enemies \Ntook away your confidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.01,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your brother was your guide on the sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that you have lost a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.39,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the toughest enemies in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,blocked your way time after time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.24,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your power is not enough to beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.15,0:18:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could be level-headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Pacifistas!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.23,0:18:41.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.94,0:18:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never find your way like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you've lost yourself \Nin regret and guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.56,0:19:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that it's painful now, Luffy,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.38,0:19:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you have to bottle up those feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.97,0:19:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just think about the ones you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.12,0:19:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't get back what you've lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.25,0:19:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it that you still have?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.05,0:20:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, don't fool around \Nhere. I'm training now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:17.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Tell everybody to take their post!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.77,0:20:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, you just see if I don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.04,0:20:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch a big one soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.62,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, it's almost ready \Nso just shut up and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.25,0:20:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy, no matter how serious your \Ninjury is, you're in good hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.24,0:20:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can teach you about archeology \Nif you're interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.85,0:20:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! The Cola engine \Nis in top shape as always!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave everything \Nabout the Sunny to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Luffy-san! It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.97,0:21:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now here is the first song for today!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.88,0:21:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.44,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.46,0:21:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.25,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:47.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.32,0:21:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.33,0:21:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zoro! Nami! Usopp! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.58,0:21:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper! Robin! Franky! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:21:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.01,0:22:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to meet them on the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.06,0:22:11.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Meet on the Sunny in three days!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.81,0:22:19.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go! It took a while but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.03,0:22:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I know that they're waiting for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What I saw there, Jimbei, was...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.19,0:22:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Older brothers can't help worrying...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.05,0:22:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...if their younger brother is weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.82,0:22:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that he'll be a handful
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.34,0:22:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but please look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy wasn't just the kid who \Nused to follow me around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.09,0:22:52.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...such reliable friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be alright no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.88,0:23:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I felt relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.40,0:23:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see them now...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.12,0:23:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.45,0:23:27.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy is missing his friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.55,0:23:30.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, far across the sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.26,0:23:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the friends he'd been separated from
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.14,0:23:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are still fighting their own battles to \Nmake it back to the Sabaody Archipelago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, news of the "War of the Best" \Nmakes its way to the separated friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.52,0:23:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.89,0:23:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Straw Hats in Shock! \NThe Bad News Has Reached Them!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.94,0:23:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
